@startuml state-contribution
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontSize 10

title Contribution Lifecycle States

[*] --> Pending : Billing cycle due date reached

Pending --> Processing : Payment initiated\nvia Stripe

Processing --> Success : Stripe confirms\npayment
Processing --> Failed : Stripe returns\nerror

Failed --> Retrying : retryCount < 3\n(retry in +2 days)
Retrying --> Processing : Retry attempt\ninitiated

Failed --> [*] : retryCount >= 3\n(membership suspended)

Success --> Refunded : Admin-initiated\nrefund
Success --> [*]
Refunded --> [*]

@enduml
